reviewText: Great "sealed condition" to replace my original.  Better than expected!
I HAVE THE ROLAND VM-3100 PRO AND THE VIDEO HELPED ME GET STARTED FASTER.  IT ALSO HELPED ME LEARN THE TERMS USED.

This is a must have for anyone new to the VM3100

The workings of VM3100, powerful asit is, can be tricky to grasp for the novice, especially if relying  upon the manuals supplied by Roland

This video is well produced and will save the new operator, a great deal of time and heartache.

Well worth the money
